lead_paragraph: Philadelphia quarterback Carson Wentz briefly left the Eagles' game in the third quarter Thursday night after taking a late hit from Giants defensive end Olivier Vernon.

headline.print_headline: Carson Wentz Returns After Leaving Game With Head Injury
